data.description: Welcome home! This charming and well-maintained home is ready for it's new owners! With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths this 1,465 sqft home is perfect to start your homeowner journey! The interior of the home features granite counter tops and stone backsplash, updated flooring and so much natural lighting. The spacious backyard with a covered patio is ready for entertainment, added Solar to make sure the home stays cool during the hot summer months is a nice plus! Don't wait to see it and call it yours!
